  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas Recap 1-13-24\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping the latest Star Atlas news.\nMetaverse Nomads #129 Star Atlas 1000 Player UE5 Stress Test\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video replay of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nMetagravity Stress test brew\nStar Atlas TV posted a video replay of the latest Atlas Brew. The event was part of the larger Star Atlas Stress live stream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #112\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas Metagravity Stress Test\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video of his experience in the Star Atlas Stress Test.\nWhy Solana MMO ‘Star Atlas’ Is Hosting a 1,000-Player Online Stress Test\nDecrypt published an article about the Star Atlas Stress Test.\nStar Atlas Stress Test Family Photo\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the family photo in the Star Atlas Stress Test.\nSTAR ATLAS #217 Missing Multiplayer Events! Because Sleep & Adult\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about updates in Star Atlas.\nStar Atlas Throwdown: Score VS Sage (Part 1)\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video comparing Star Atlas SCORE to SAGE.",
